Your privacy is important to us
We will never give your email address or any personal details to any third party.
Your email address will only be used for the purposes of contacting you in relation to the cuespeak product and associated speech therapy materials.
Session sharing stores your session on our servers for up to 7 days. While this information is mainly about the exercise settings that control how Cuespeak is configured for you, it will also include any personalised content you may have entered. We advise to not use personally identifying or sensitive information here.